  <brief_title>Evaluation of an Organizational Model for Remote Monitoring of Pacemaker and Implantable Cardioverter Defibrillator Recipients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Registry for the Evaluation of an Organizational Model for Remote Monitoring of Pacemaker and Implantable Cardioverter Defibrillator (ICD) Recipients in the Clinical Practice</official_title>
